title: Frederick County Sheriff’s Office looking for a missing 17-year-old last seen May 2
body: FREDERICK COUNTY, Md. — The Frederick County Sheriff’s Office is looking for a missing 17-year-old Enyla Lyne Thomas. She was last seen on May 2 around 6:00 p.m. in the 9200 block of Ridgefield Circle. She's 5’4”, 165 lbs with brown hair and brown eyes and was last seen wearing a white shirt, black shorts and hot pink and white sneakers. Enyla also has a gold nose piercing and a tattoo of a dollar sign on the webbing of her hand. If anyone has any information regarding her whereabouts, please contact the Frederick County Sheriff’s Office at (301)-600-1046, CASE# 21-040130.
